#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/writing-native-applications-tips.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Managing Proxy Classes"
msgstr "管理代理类"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/writing-native-applications-tips.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "While writing native application you'll need to define proxy classes at image build time by specifying the list of interfaces that they implement."
msgstr "在编写本地应用程序时，您需要在构建映像时定义代理类，指定它们实现的接口列表。"

#. type: Plain text
